videos.description: Yellow Jackets' TaQuon Marshall runs 1 yard for a touchdown to give Georgia Tech an early lead over Virginia.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech punches it in for a TD

videos.description: Yellow Jackets' Antonio Simmons is left unguarded and blocks Lester Coleman's punt, giving Georgia Tech the ball with great field position.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Simmons blocks punt

videos.description: Cavaliers' Olamide Zaccheaus is stripped by the Yellow Jackets' Bruce Jordan-Swilling who also then recovers the ball for Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: Virginia has costly fumble

videos.description: Yellow Jackets' KirVonte Benson jumps over the pile into the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown to pad Georgia Tech's lead.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Benson jumps into the end zone

videos.description: Joe Reed finds a gap and returns the Yellow Jackets' kick for a 92-yard touchdown to chip away at Georgia Tech's lead.
videos.headline: Virginia's Reed breaks free for a 92-yard kick return TD

videos.description: On the first play of the third quarter, Yellow Jackets' TaQuon Marshall finds a gap and burst for a 78-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech scores quickly in second half with long TD

videos.description: Cavaliers' Kurt Benkert's pass is intercepted by Bruce Jordan-Swilling who returns it for a 27-yard touchdown to extend Georgia Tech's lead.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Jordan-Swilling snags pick-six

videos.description: Cavaliers' Kurt Benkert lobs it deep to an open Andre Levrone for a 34-yard touchdown to cut into the Yellow Jackets' lead.
videos.headline: Benkert connects with Levrone for Virginia TD

videos.description: Cavaliers' Kurt Benkert finds Doni Dowling in the back of the end zone for a 28-yard touchdown. Virginia would successfully make a two-point conversion to tie game.
videos.headline: Virginia scores TD to cut Georgia Tech's lead

videos.description: Cavaliers' Brenton Nelson makes a diving catch to pick off TaQuon Marshall's pass.
videos.headline: Virginia's Nelson makes diving interception

videos.description: Yellow Jackets QB TaQuon Marshall fumbles in the end zone, resulting in a safety for Virginia.
videos.headline: Virginia increases lead with safety

videos.description: Yellow Jackets' TaQuon Marshall throws it 33 yards to Ricky Jeune for a touchdown. Georgia Tech would successfully make a two-point conversion to take a 37-34 late in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Marshall passes deep TD pass
